text: Elimination Chamber (2013) (also known as No Escape (2013) in Germany) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view show made by WWE. It took place on February 17, 2013 at New Orleans Arena in New Orleans, Louisiana. It was the fourth Elimination Chamber event held by WWE. The main event saw The Rock defeat CM Punk to keep his WWE Championship.
